00:43:59.284 --> 00:44:00.243
Unbelievable.

00:44:01.744 --> 00:44:02.871
Here.

00:44:05.915 --> 00:44:07.584
Geez, what the hell?

00:44:13.923 --> 00:44:15.842
What is wrong with him?

00:44:17.135 --> 00:44:20.263
Don't they sell anything sharper
than cotton candy here?

00:44:21.139 --> 00:44:22.724
I swear, I'm going to kill him.

00:44:23.808 --> 00:44:24.642
Ms. Seo!

00:44:29.439 --> 00:44:30.690
Why'd you come to this town?

00:44:31.441 --> 00:44:33.735
I'm here for work, obviously.

00:44:34.402 --> 00:44:36.362
Then just do your job and leave.

00:44:36.446 --> 00:44:38.281
Why are you hitting on a single mom?

00:44:38.364 --> 00:44:39.991
Hitting on her?

