In Seoul,
this is what we call a "situationship."

00:44:43.953 --> 00:44:45.497
A "situationship"?

00:44:45.580 --> 00:44:47.081
Darn it.

00:44:47.165 --> 00:44:48.541
Why are you doing this?

00:44:48.625 --> 00:44:50.210
You better not be lying,

00:44:50.752 --> 00:44:53.213
or this will turn into
a whole different "situation."

00:44:53.296 --> 00:44:54.631
Understand? Believe it or not,

00:44:55.215 --> 00:44:58.593
I'm the one and only PE teacher
at Shinsu High.

00:44:59.260 --> 00:45:01.179
Hye-suk!

00:45:01.262 --> 00:45:02.847
-Hye-suk!
-Keep it down.

00:45:04.974 --> 00:45:07.769
Gosh, he's driving me crazy.
What's gotten into him?

00:45:18.363 --> 00:45:19.989
Maybe it's the nice weather.

00:45:20.073 --> 00:45:21.783
It's unusually crowded here today.

00:45:22.867 --> 00:45:25.078
This won't do, let's go somewhere else.

00:45:28.289 --> 00:45:29.874
What's going on today?

00:45:43.346 --> 00:45:44.305
You see,

00:45:45.890 --> 00:45:48.560
